{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2244","heading":"Security investigations","label":"2244 Security investigations","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptIV/ch134/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2244","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments1991—Subsec. (a)(1), (2). substituted “Government” for “government”.Pub. L. 102–190"],"amendments":["Amendments1991—Subsec. (a)(1), (2). substituted “Government” for “government”.Pub. L. 102–190"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":null,"label":"a","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2244%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2244%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"That a current, complete investigation file is not available from any other department or agency of the Federal Government with respect to that individual or facility.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2244%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"That no other department or agency of the Federal Government is conducting an investigation with respect to that individual or facility that could be used as the basis for determining whether to grant the security clearance.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":null,"label":"b","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2244","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2244%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For purposes of subsection (a)(1), a current investigation file is a file on an investigation that has been conducted within the past five years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
